  <description><![CDATA[<p>The charming Hotel Sylvana offers a peaceful, welcoming stay in Mayrhofen. The hotel prides itself on being a family-run hotel and caters to other families and couples with an excellent level of service. We love the attention to detail at the hotel, you will find plenty of family memorabilia and nice touches throughout the hotel and rooms.</p>
<h2>Peaceful location</h2>
<p>Wake up to the sounds of nature while still being just a short walk from the bustling centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/f9068cb62c4d4b2299a0ef29fd676ed5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f9068cb62c4d4b2299a0ef29fd676ed5}" title="Mayrhofen">Mayrhofen</a>. The Hotel Sylvana has the best of both worlds with peaceful surroundings just moments away from the famous après and great slopes of Mayrhofen.</p>
<p>This family-run hotel welcomes guests with warm Austrian hospitality and a cosy ambiance. You can enjoy incredible views of the Zillertal Valley from your balcony too.</p>
<p>The ski bus stops just five minutes from the hotel, or you can walk to the centre of resort in 15 minutes.</p>
<h2>Cosy dining</h2>
<p><span>Breakfast is taken in the hotel's own sunny breakfast room with hot and cold buffet options. For dinner guests head to the <a data-udi="umb://document/df19749344dd46cc96a029c614eb201e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/df19749344dd46cc96a029c614eb201e}" title="Hotel Berghof">Hotel Berghof</a> for a four course meal. Just a five minute walk from Hotel Sylvana, the Hotel Berghof offers excellent food with an emphasis on sustainability which means great food made with local produce.</span></p>
<p>The hotel's bar is a great place to relax with a drink after dinner, with a honesty bar system.<span></span></p>
<h2>Alpine retreat</h2>
<p><span>Rooms are all decorated with the hotel's own unique flair. All rooms have balconies with excellent views towards the mountains or down the valley. You can expect spacious rooms which cosy homely touches.</span></p>
<p><span>There is a small spa area with everything you need to relax after a day on the slopes. Warm up in the sauna and steam room, or chill out in the relaxation room.</span></p>
<h3>Why is this is an Inghams' Choice property?</h3>
<p><strong>Family-run</strong> - Excellent personal service is what the Hotel Sylvana is known for and you will receive a warm welcome on arrival and helpful staff throughout your stay.</p>
<p><strong>Value for money</strong> - At the Hotel Sylvana you get the best of both worlds, a family-run small hotel with half board in a 4* hotel just down the road.</p>
<p><strong>Peaceful location</strong> - You will be surrounded by peaceful forests and nature while being just a short walk from the lively centre of Mayrhofen. </p>]]></description>
